{"tid":863203,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【無欲無求】周潤發Lifestyle空前絕後","createTime":"2018-10-15T11:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T17:55:48.000Z","uid":49391,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"373dfecba501867f9d1819e3ba5e8c1573a5755a","tid":863203,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFOLdny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFOLdny.jpg&h=f388165f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巨星周潤發接受訪時談到他的捐款計劃，準備將自己的全部財產56億港元捐給慈善機構。發哥稱每月僅花費6000多元，兩年前仍用着舊式手提電話，並用上了17年，才開始轉用智能手機，就算買衫都常在折扣店選購。他說：「我不為別人穿衣服，只要我覺得它很舒服，那對我來說就足夠了。」<br />\n<br />\n其妻子陳薈蓮亦於數年前，為了支持發哥而建立了慈善機構，發哥笑說：「錢不是我的，我只是暫時保管它。」並稱錢並不是幸福的源泉：「我的夢想是成為一個幸福和正常的人。生活中最難的事情不是你賺多少錢，而是如何保持一種平和的心態，以一種簡單而無憂無慮的方式度過餘生。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181015/bkn-20181015065610712-1015_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181015%2Fbkn-20181015065610712-1015_00862_001.html&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2BjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a8c4644e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181015/bkn-20181015065610712-1015_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3c0034680e16a8dfb42fd884fd721f2f880fc5a2","tid":863203,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:01:16.000Z","msg":"發哥好似幾時都咁後生咁有活力<br />\n可能真係關心境事"},{"pid":"79e67bbbdb3afd581718187b20dc85a0466d0f7f","tid":863203,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:04:31.000Z","msg":"咩電話用到17年"},{"pid":"6ddd8441a3b34166e131b9756feab9c8f7fea7a6","tid":863203,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79e67bbbdb3afd581718187b20dc85a0466d0f7f","tid":863203,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:04:31.000Z","msg":"咩電話用到17年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:06:43.000Z","msg":"NOKIA"}